				<h3><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100914063926/http://www.eu-russiacentre.org/news/russian-irish-presidents-discuss-osce-cooperation-moscow.html">Russian, Irish presidents to discuss OSCE cooperation in Moscow</a></h3>
