				<h3><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100914063926/http://www.eu-russiacentre.org/news/belarus-lithuania-ukraine-work-eastern-partnership-program.html">Belarus, Lithuania, Ukraine to work on Eastern Partnership program</a></h3>
		<span class="Tags">
			<b>09 Sep 2010</b>
